parameters:
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>*panting*...panting*...So, that concludes today's course...
Thank you for your hard work.

\nc<Customer>Good work~ Wow~, it's been a while since I've had so much
fun.

\nc<Customer>It was a bit awkward, but your earnestness... It's like I'm
feeling the thrill of a beginner again, you know?

\nc<Saki>(Did he... misunderstand the meaning of 'beginner'?) So you
noticed after all...

\nc<Customer>I'm a veteran, you know. Don't be so down about it. It was
really good. Saki-chan, you might have a talent for being a
succubus.

\nc<Saki>Talent for being a succubus... I've been aware of it for
some time, but it feels strange to be told that to my face.

\nc<Customer>Shh. If you get a tip, won't the company confiscate it? Just
tuck it away secretly. There are cameras here too, you
know...

\nc<Saki>Eeeeh...\bustMsgExp[1, 5] Thank you so much! (I would
usually refuse, but with my current financial situation,
there's no way...)
